&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;添加shell脚本&#34;&gt;添加shell脚本
&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在左侧搜索 “运行 Shell 脚本”（Run Shell Script）。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC.png&#34;
	width=&#34;2000&#34;
	height=&#34;1768&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC_hu781375108408735742.png 480w, https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC_hu14615199015857252835.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;alt text&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;113&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;271px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;拖动到右侧工作区。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E6%8B%96%E5%8A%A8shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1998&#34;
	height=&#34;1756&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E6%8B%96%E5%8A%A8shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7_hu11765521415516910728.png 480w, https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E6%8B%96%E5%8A%A8shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7_hu11696295268397146098.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;alt text&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;113&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;273px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在 Shell 选项里，选择 /bin/bash（或 /bin/zsh）。
&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9shell%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1220&#34;
	height=&#34;356&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9shell%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B_hu16876359859905355104.png 480w, https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9shell%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B_hu10732417014375881329.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;alt text&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;342&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;822px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;在文本框里输入如下代码：&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#!/bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;/opt/homebrew/Cellar/jadx/1.5.1/bin/jadx-gui
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://example.com/p/mac%E4%B8%8B%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%86%99%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%A1%AB%E4%B8%8A%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9.png&#34;
